{"tid":635153,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中興通訊：不能接受美國商務部制裁","createTime":"2018-04-20T01:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T09:17:41.000Z","uid":62646,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"70dfe5f065bb458ddc1ba9815e394bdde2c4d838","tid":635153,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T01:42:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/7x24/2018-04-20/detail-ifznefkf4157044.d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F7x24%2F2018-04-20%2Fdetail-ifznefkf4157044.d.html&d=08y%2BzYbygTJWdXbBzO%2BZJCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=7ee9dbc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/7x24/2018-04-20/detail-ifznefkf4157044.d.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中興通訊：不能接受美國商務部制裁】中興通訊4月20日聲明指出，美國商務部工業與安全局無視中興通訊過去兩年在遵循出口管制合規方面的艱苦努力、巨大投入和長足進步；無視上述兩份函件中的問題是公司自查發現，及時主動通報；無視公司第一時間處理了對此可能有疏忽的責任人，並快速糾正問題，並聘請權威美國律所獨立調查。在相關調查尚未結束之前，BIS執意對公司施以最嚴厲的制裁，對中興通訊極不公平，中興通訊不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/094234_e71fa93122d06e2d137589add2661918.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F094234_e71fa93122d06e2d137589add2661918.png&h=2a1ccc38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9c3bbe4b3b0677027126ff4b301602384ac1e3d","tid":635153,"uid":74281,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T01:44:35.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 賺咁撚多呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7fbb84ca2d8c592f834be2c07db2c8940530d9","tid":635153,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"唔接受咪話俾老師知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a78fd74c98290571a7aef2a5b03684f7e5ed857","tid":635153,"uid":2772,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"主客都未識分"},{"pid":"f3e49fa9cac8cc918ffade9ae44f036f3511e2bf","tid":635153,"uid":44486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score